PRINT HOST NAME : hostname

CHECK PERMISSIONS OF FOLDER OR FILE : getfacl /Path/To/Folder/File 

LIST WITH INODE NUMBER : ls -i

PERMANENT DELETION OF FILE WITH NO RECOVERY : shred -u Filename OR shred --remove Filename

CHECK SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE : 
    
    sudo dmidecode 
    
    lscpu

GET TYPE OF FILE : file Filename

LIST USB DEVICES CONNECTED : lsusb





